# Post req to impersonate an account on buildbear sandbox

```json
{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "hardhat_impersonateAccount",
  "params": ["0xf1da173228fcf015f43f3ea15abbb51f0d8f1123"],
  "id": 1
}
```

# Post req to set byte code of a contract

```json
{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "hardhat_setCode",
  "params": [
    "0x6B175474E89094C44Da98b954EedeAC495271d0F",
    ""
  ],
  "id": 1
}
```
